===Etymology===
For [[w:Johannes Kepler|Johannes Kepler]] German mathematician and astronomer
===Noun===
'''Kepler's equation'''
#{{mathematics}},{{astronomy}} the [[mathematical]] [[relationship]] between the [[mean anomaly]] and the [[eccentric anomaly]] of a [[planet]] in an [[elliptical]] [[orbit]]
